[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "おーい！　イェルカ、シトリン！\nこっちよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01165",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "ちょっと。そっちが呼んだくせに\n遅れて来るってどういう神経してるわけ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01166",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ごめん……キューンとヤドヴィガと話してたら、\n思いのほか盛り上がっちゃって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01167",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "へえ！　仲良しでいいじゃないか！\nなんか昔を思い出すねぇ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01168",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "そういえば、昔はよくナナとヤドヴィガとキューンで\n集まって、内緒話とかしてたよねぇ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01169",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "そうそう。次の任務がめんどくさいーとか、\n調合疲れるーとか、ゴゥが暑苦しいーとか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01170",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "あははっ、ゴゥってばかわいそ～。\nま、暑苦しいのは同意するけどさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01171",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あれ？　内緒話なのに、\nなんで二人とも内容を知ってるのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01172",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "あっはっは！\nま、細かいことはいいじゃないか！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01173",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ヴァレリアが今日、アタシたちを呼んだのは\nヘル兄の話をするためだろう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01174",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "イェルカも話が早いわね！\nもしかして、誰かから何か聞いた？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01175",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "リーベからちょいとね。\n情報共有に抜かりがない、できた妹だよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01176",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "他のみんなから、ヘル兄が怖いだの厳しいだのって\n話は散々聞いただろうから、アタシからは違うことを",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01177",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ヘル兄は、一番初めに創られたホムンクルスだ。\n脅威に対抗するために、大きな力を持って生まれた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01178",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "だから、兄弟たちを力で支配するのは当たり前、\nみたいなことを言いたいわけ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01179",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "違うよシトリン。話は最後まで聞くものさ。\n聞かないのは粋じゃないよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01180",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ヘル兄とゼロ姉の関係を思い出してみてほしいんだ。\n長兄と、その１つ下の妹。仲がいいと思わないかい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01181",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そうね。なんかゼロってヘルトの言うことは聞くし、\n特に懐いているような気がするわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01182",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "その理由は、ヘル兄が自分より強いから\nというのもあると思うけれど――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01183",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "一番は、ヘル兄がゼロ姉の面倒をよく見ていたから、\nだと思うのさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01184",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そうなの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01185",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ああ。これはずっと前に、\nアウグストから聞いた話なんだけれど――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01186",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ゼロ姉が創られた時、ヘル兄は初めての兄弟に\nとっても喜んでいたらしいんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01187",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "それで、鍛錬も食事も休息も一緒に行って、\n兄として、ゼロ姉に色々教えてあげていたって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01188",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "……あのヘルトが？\n想像できないんだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01189",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "本当さ。アタシは３番目として生まれてから\n少しの間、二人のこと近くで見てたけれど――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01190",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ヘル兄は、ゼロ姉がケガしたら薬を塗ってあげたり、\n食後すぐ寝るゼロ姉を寝所まで運んであげたりしてたね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01191",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "だからアタシも最初はゼロ姉よろしく面倒見られて、\nヘル兄に髪の毛を結ってもらったりしてたさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01192",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "シトリンにもそういうの、あっただろう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01193",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "いや？　僕はゼロたちと違って、生まれた直後から\n一人前だったからね。そういうのはなかったし――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01194",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "隠さなくていいだろう？　昔は食べるの下手くそで、\n汚れた口周りを拭いてもらったりしてたじゃないか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01195",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "あああーーー！！！\n妹の前で言わなくていいんだよ！　そんなことは！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01196",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あはは！　お姉ちゃんたちのそういう話を\n聞くのって、なんか楽しいわね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01197",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "他のみんなからも話を聞いて思ったんだけど、\nヘルトって昔はしっかりいいお兄ちゃんしていたのね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01198",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "「昔は」？　いやいや、それは違う。\n根っこは変わっていないとアタシは思うよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01199",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "とにかく、ヘルトはやりすぎなんだよ。\n長兄としての自負からかもしれないけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01200",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "どんな理由があったとしても、\n恐怖で支配してくる兄なんて僕はごめんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01201",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（昔のヘルトは、今からは想像できないほどちゃんと\n　お兄ちゃんで、兄弟たちからも慕われている……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01202",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（だとしたらどうして、\n　今の歪な兄弟関係ができてしまったのかしら）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01203",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ここに、ヘルトが今の状態になった理由が\n　ありそうな気がするわ……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01204",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]